<article id="post-2915" class="post-2915 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general tag-health">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2011/04/my-first-surgery/" rel="bookmark">My first surgery</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Yesterday, I finally got my hernia repaired. (&#8220;Repair&#8221;, incidentally, is what the surgery is called.) It&#8217;s a short job that uses, believe it or not, part of a screen door.<br />
It wasn&#8217;t a procedure that I was particularly looking forward to &#8212; the thought of surgery was more than a little frightening &#8212; but I&#8217;m sure I&#8217;ll be glad to have had.<br />
Y&#8217;know, once all this pain subsides&#8230;<br />
 <a href="http://geoff.wp/2011/04/my-first-surgery/#more-2915" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> &#8220;My first surgery&#8221;</span></a></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=49&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r' srcset='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/095609f98b14811f33ecac14add504b3?s=98&#038;d=mm&#038;r=r 2x' class='avatar avatar-49 photo' height='49' width='49' loading='lazy'/><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="http://geoff.wp/author/sonworf/">Geoff</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/2011/04/my-first-surgery/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published updated" datetime="2011-04-16T12:46:46-06:00">16 April 2011</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/category/general/" rel="category tag">General</a></span><span class="tags-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Tags </span><a href="http://geoff.wp/tag/health/" rel="tag">health</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2011/04/my-first-surgery/#comments">2 Comments<span class="screen-reader-text"> on My first surgery</span></a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
